data.description: Sky Mesa is the Best Community in south Meridian! Sky Mesa is a well-established community with mature landscaping and proven value. This is the final phase of more than a decade of home building and best-in-class community design. We've created amenities for an active lifestyle, with two infinity-edge community pools that offer BBQ and picnic areas, full-court outdoor basketball, community parks and green spaces, and miles of walkable paths all in a perfect location in Meridian, ID with safety and freedom top of mind. This is a brand new home ready for Feb. 2023! Call to schedule a visit.
